Author: stegasaurus-
Text: if you’re anywhere near soho there’s sooo many vegan restaurants up that way, if you chuck it into google you’re likely to be able to find at least one place that has a calorie count. Franco mancas is an italian chain across london, i’m p sure they don’t have calorie counts but if you’re able too i would really make the exception, their vegan options are great and franco mancas is just life lol it’s probs my favourite restaurant! good luck☺️
